thedral is <strong>free to visit<\/strong> and although it might look busy, the inside offers plenty of space so the line is a short wait.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14457&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134722\/things-to-do-florence-italy.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134722\/things-to-do-florence-italy-20x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134722\/things-to-do-florence-italy-398x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"8 Best Things To Do in Florence, Italy\" height=\"600\" width=\"398\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It is one of the largest cathedrals in the world and the world&#x2019;s largest dome! Visitors are allowed on the top of the dome to have an incredible city view but it takes 460+ steps to climb to get there. Tickets to climb the Duomo sell out weeks in advance so if you&#x2019;re wanting to do it definitely plan ahead and book.  <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/tickets-duomo-florence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get your tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/things-to-do-florence-italy-Cathedral-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do florence italy Cathedral\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do florence italy Cathedral\" class=\"wp-image-14504 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134733\/things-to-do-florence-italy-Cathedral-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134733\/things-to-do-florence-italy-Cathedral-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134733\/things-to-do-florence-italy-Cathedral-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134733\/things-to-do-florence-italy-Cathedral-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134733\/things-to-do-floren