t Gelato<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cross the Ponte Vecchio, turn right and wander through the beautiful streets on the other side of the river. This part is less visited and a nice getaway from the busy streets. Make your way to Ponte Alla Carraia, but before you cross the bridge, get a delicious Gelato at <a aria-label=\"(opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/K3UgexUNWFE3HJzs7\">Gelateria La Carraia<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/florence-italy-best-gelato.jpg\" alt=\"florence italy best gelato\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"308\" alt=\"florence italy best gelato\" class=\"wp-image-14502 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-600x410.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-450x308.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-800x547.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-1080x739.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134736\/florence-italy-best-gelato-263x180.jpg 263w, https:\/\/st