<h3>6. Santa Croce<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Piazza Santa Croce and the Santa Croce Basilica are a little more between the locals. Cafes and street performers are making the square, even more, an excellent place to sit down, relax, and absorb the charming Florence vibe for a bit.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Find all:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/florence-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Hotels in Florence<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/things-to-do-florence-Santa-Croce-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do florence Santa Croce\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do florence Santa Croce\" class=\"wp-image-14486 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134824\/things-to-do-florence-Santa-Croce-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134824\/things-to-do-florence-Santa-Croce-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134824\/things-to-do-florence-Santa-Croce-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134824\/things-to-do-florence-Santa-Croce-261x33