\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>By train<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Florence is easy to reach by train as the city is well-connected to all major stations in Italy. The international airport offers direct flights to many European cities. Getting from <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/italy\/rome\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rome<\/a> to Florence only takes 80 minutes with the high-speed railway line.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/italy-train-tickets\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Find your train tickets here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find your train tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/florence-train.jpg\" alt=\"florence train\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"florence train\" class=\"wp-image-14499 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134747\/florence-train.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134747\/florence-train-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23134747\/florence-train-600x400.jpg 600w,